      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_05_01-mei003.m4a",
      "text": "月ストのみんなのイメージを伝えただけで\nこんなにいっぱいアイデアを出せるなんて！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Just by conveying the image of the Moon Tempest members‚\nThey can come up with so many ideas!",
