      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_05_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "（ビーチでのイベントのため、新しい夏用衣装の意見を）\n（みんなに聞いているんだが……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Seeking opinions on new summer outfits for the beach event…）\n（Asking everyone…）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 27.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_05_01-mei004.m4a",
      "text": "うーん……あ\nこの衣装可愛いけど、この部分はいらないかも",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hmm… Ah!\nThis outfit is cute‚ but maybe this part isn't necessary.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 33.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_05_01-mei005.m4a",
      "text": "こっちは踊るのに邪魔になっちゃうかな～\nここを取って～、こっちももっとスッキリさせて～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It might get in the way when I dance…\nIf we remove this part and make this area cleaner…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 42.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_05_01-mei006.m4a",
      "text": "動きやすさも考えないとだし……そうだ！\nここからここまですっぱりカットしちゃうとか！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We also need to consider ease of movement… Oh yes!\nWe can just cut it from here to here and make it more streamlined!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 53.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
